§I SOVEREIGNTY-NOTES
  ⟦
    13-axes are moral-engine NOT identity-marker
    NEVER shame · NEVER score-as-good-or-bad
    every axis-direction is VALID (e.g. forgotten-side-of-MEMORY isn't bad)
    visual-color-map is INFORMATION not JUDGEMENT
    user-can-override LOA_AXIS_COLOR_OVERRIDE=<json>
  ⟧

